1.0.name: wordpress/custom-fields-for-many-dates
1.0.description:
This plugin will allow a user to add/edit/delete up to 10 custom dates using an easy to use datepicker.

The user will also be able to select a title for each of these dates. Outputting this data to a wordpress site in a customized fashion will take some knowledge of the Wordpress database.
